Name: Splash Fly Fire
About the game: Flappy Fly Fire is a game in which you need to control fire. The gameplay is simple. His flight is jets of flame, which the fire lifts up. Thus it is necessary to fly through dynamites and try not to blow them up. The game ends when the fire touches the dynamite and everything explodes.
